entries.npc_11: I don't generally kill dumb animals, but you're making it difficult to keep that rule.  No more talking.
entries.npc_10: Not unless you keep it up.  Get out of my sight and live a while longer.
entries.player_9: Are you going to kill me?
entries.npc_5: I recommend finding something else to do then.  It would be safer for you.
entries.npc_9: I pity people like you.  Or I would if I cared.
entries.npc_8: I'll just be on my way then.
entries.npc_4: Unless you weren't planning to live long I suggest you knock off the questions.
entries.npc_3: I'm just fine on my own.  Don't you have anything better to do than bother me?
entries.npc_7: Sorry, I don't talk to fools.
entries.npc_2: My name is Mara Jade.  That is all you need to know.
entries.npc_1: I've got things to do, so if you want to talk make it quick.
